Rating: 4
Delicious! When dealing with leftover turkey, my expectations are pretty low, but this is a recipe I'll make many times in the future. I used chicken broth instead of water, craisins instead of raisins and concocted my own pumpkin pie spice (50% cinnamon, 25% allspice, 25% ground cloves). Very very tasty, and a nice change from the Thanksgiving leftovers that everyone was getting tired of.

